<p>
  To publish, run <code>cargo publish</code> after setting up your crates.io API token. Make sure your <code>Cargo.toml</code> has all required fields: <code>name</code>, <code>version</code>, <code>description</code>, <code>license</code>, and <code>repository</code>.
</p>

<h3>2. GitHub Releases (Everyone)</h3>

