  <li>Add a <code>watch</code> mode using the <code>notify</code> crate that re-runs searches when files change</li>
  <li>Build a TUI (terminal user interface) with <code>ratatui</code> for interactive file browsing</li>
  <li>Publish to crates.io and set up the GitHub Actions release pipeline</li>
</ul>

